text: Dreaming of Rita () is a 1993 Swedish Finnish comedy movie directed by Jon Lindström and starring Marika Lagercrantz, Philip Zandén, Yaba Holst, Adam Blänning, Per Oscarsson, Gert Fylking. ==Other websites== * Category:1993 comedy movies Category:Swedish comedy movies Category:Finnish movies Category:Movies directed by Jon Lindström
